
**a figure of speech which denies to an object one of its own attributes and ascribes another which is foreign to it**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   ஒழிப்பணி
-


**which ascribes products to places where they are not found as pears to the mountain or gold to the sea**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   இடமலைவு
-

